      public int compareTo​(Order o)
      This compareTo override orders by DateResolved (and secondarily by ID) because this is useful for the historical price system
      Specified by:
      compareTo in interface java.lang.Comparable<Order>
      Parameters:
      o - other order
      Returns:
      For two resolved orders with different DateResolved values, the older transaction is less Otherwise, the lower ID is less
